data.description: Looking for a cozy updated home at a great price?? I've got one for you!! This charming home is centrally located in Corpus Christi. Offers 4 spacious bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms and an open concept. Kitchen is fully equiped with stainless steel appliances (gas stove), and refrigerator also conveys with this home. Flooring in home is a little over a year old. Roof was installed in 2012. Let's not forget the spacious backyard and no back neighbors that can provide a little more privacy. Additionally, being centrally located offers more convenience to local grocery stores, shopping and easier access to major roads. So don't let this beauty get away! Call your local agent to view this home!
